profile_positions.description:
CO2 char gasification using catalyst mixtures
Reduced temperature required for CO production by 10% via cost-effective iron catalyst addition.
Identified iron catalyst transformations during gasification using FTIR and SEM to avoid deactivation of catalyst.

Data-Driven Analysis of Turbulent Flame Images
Designed, trained, and tested a CNN model in Python to classify unburned pockets with an average accuracy of 90% and reducing processing time by 80%.

Designed and numerically validated the interfaces subjected to high-temperature increasing O-rings life by 400%.

Laminar condensation on a non-isothermal wall/sphere

Developed a backward finite difference scheme to solve the modeled equation.

Flame spread rate over a pool of aviation fuel 
Simulated fuel stratification of top of a pool of aviation fuel using ANSYS Fluent identifying the required height for successful laser spark ignition.
Analytically modeled the gas flame spread rate with an error of ~5% using Navier Stokes equations.
